description: Hiking lake O'hara area in summer is absolutely amazing, so is cross country skiing to it. The view is spectacular and totally different from that in summer: huge snow mountain, snow pines, ice lakes: everything is in white except those colorful cabins.
directions: The trail head is just the famous O'hara shuttle bus stop. It is 10km west of the crossing of highway #93 with highway #1.
title: Lake O'hara & lake Mary & Elizabeth hut
